# Security Policy â€“ DroneCommand Pro

## Supported Versions
Security updates apply to the latest production version only.

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you discover a security issue, contact:
security@eaglesightdroneintelligence.com

Please include:
- Description of the issue
- Steps to reproduce
- Potential impact
- Suggested fix (optional)

We respond within 72 hours.

## Responsible Disclosure
Do NOT publicly disclose vulnerabilities without written approval.

## Forbidden Activities
Users may not:
- Run automated scanners
- Attempt privilege escalation
- Exploit API endpoints
- Perform load testing without permission

Violations may result in immediate termination and reporting to authorities.
